{"tid":1453232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（失物）有個傻仔係機場發現唔見咗嘢","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T07:35:43.000Z","uid":67217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e07993bf2878fec5e0ca672bb0701f72566bed56","tid":1453232,"uid":67217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:36:49.000Z","msg":"有個傻仔係8月10號係機場發現唔見咗個啡色卡套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個傻仔就係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前日係大埔發完夢之後就落咗沙田搭E42轉咗去機場和你飛 大概6點半落車 之後走個時發現唔見咗個啡色Kangol卡套 入面有我身份證 學生證 八達通同信用卡 我上車個陣仲係到 所以應該係車上面或者機場到唔見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲幫下手 個卡套有曬我所有證件 同埋唔想補領張新身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n知呢兩日都有更重要既po要出 唔想個po咁快沉 所以今日先開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有人執到可唔可以tg我 @FairyBanana<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可！</span>"},{"pid":"c6a1658a42bfbf860a3e862fbe7769585bed1a8e","tid":1453232,"uid":209393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:37:33.000Z","msg":"推呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1點去機場！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1202a7daf183a81191e69d06f2f7dff18a52cd77","tid":1453232,"uid":67217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:39:05.000Z","msg":"1點鐘機場！"},{"pid":"c999581e980657e99efd440eb0ac1506b327c81f","tid":1453232,"uid":86614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:41:08.000Z","msg":"推"},